Title: Gauss-Codazzi Formalism to Braneworld Scenario within Brans-Dicke Theory
Authors: M. C. B. Abdalla and M. E. X. Guimaraes and J. M. Hoff da Silva
Abstract: We apply the Gauss-Codacci formalism to brane worlds scenario within the framework of Brans-Dicke gravity. The compactification is taken from six to five dimensions in order to formalize brane-world models with hybrid compactification in scalar-tensor theories.
